snippet.title: Jotunnslayer: Hordes of Hel | Early Access Release Date Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Step into the fiery chaos of Muspelheim in the latest Jotunnslayer: Hordes of Hel EA Release Date Announcement Trailer! Witness the relentless battleground of flames, where scorching terrain and ruthless enemies await. This epic preview also reveals the long-awaited Early Access launch date—January 21, 2025!

Prepare to harness the power of 4 legendary heroes, call upon 4 mighty gods, and conquer 2 maps, including the brand-new, fiery Muspelheim.

Are you ready to rise as the Jotunnslayer?

Mark your calendars for Early Access on January 21, 2025!
